{"tid":205491,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［金庸撚入］如果要比，楊過勁啲定張無忌","createTime":"2017-04-17T21:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T14:36:31.000Z","uid":5288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b52cb9e19a2d640a8e2ca4c686298cde633d9bb","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:48:25.000Z","msg":"雖然楊過係好撚勁，單手拎玄鐵重劍<br />\n但張無忌又識醫又學咗好幾味秘笈<br />\n有無金庸撚入嚟交流下<br />\n真心想吹下水，不求罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb64572ed00d96e33c487bedc99bf674d740ed7a","tid":205491,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6672a2bf1afe524e34cb510e067d44483790830","tid":205491,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:54:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e2527a7f9467937a0ebfcaf80d600f36046c652","tid":205491,"uid":106925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:55:14.000Z","msg":"武功方面楊過學得比較多，但張無忌嘅內功就強好多"},{"pid":"9203d5007307420de363d1c34721b02f93073615","tid":205491,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:55:48.000Z","msg":"無忌係打持久戰，輸出高又有保血技，打後期楊過一定輸，楊過要win一定要玩一波流"},{"pid":"e74bf8b4b15e67ba4d38643474acaee3328d793e","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>武功方面楊過學得比較多，但張無忌嘅內功就強好多</blockquote><br />\n武功係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但無忌好幾派嘅秘笈都上哂身喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56d93640bb8092d7547f83cc99d0cd0f8cd6d73","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999年接受香港報章採訪時，記者：「金庸先生，你認為在你的小說中，哪一位主角的武功最高強？」金庸回：「很大可能是張無忌。集各家之長，應該比較全面。」<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/om6lo3m.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fculture%2Fom6lo3m.html&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2d25e2c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/om6lo3m.html</a></blockquote><br />\n屌 無google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實r下水吹啫<br />\n身邊無朋友睇武俠小說<br />\n我就先睇神雕，後睇鹿鼎，啱啱睇完倚天<br />\n而家好撚著迷 想開射雕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0fc608a73450252dbc3eff0d2ad14aa6f845c2","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1999年接受香港報章採訪時，記者：「金庸先生，你認為在你的小說中，哪一位主角的武功最高強？」金庸回：「很大可能是張無忌。集各家之長，應該比較全面。」<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/om6lo3m.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fculture%2Fom6lo3m.html&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2d25e2c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/culture/om6lo3m.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人都係比較鍾意無忌哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但楊過係公認神級 唔敢得罪其他巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁開心 打和啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪啊，我都有種感覺係楊過公認好勁<br />\n但睇完神雕同倚天又覺得好似張無忌厚料啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcf7aba62fd05f70df8ecf662a86ad566b0cdd7","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無忌係打持久戰，輸出高又有保血技，打後期楊過一定輸，楊過要win一定要玩一波流</blockquote><br />\n打機mode"},{"pid":"4f919ece540421c32661a60302ff2f681c87291f","tid":205491,"uid":68208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:12:41.000Z","msg":"無忌哥哥乾坤大挪移都夠做啦"},{"pid":"afe3679d4f2593719e65646d22f2696792c71130","tid":205491,"uid":78773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:13:48.000Z","msg":"令狐沖"},{"pid":"1fcc16312f5e18c995892c18a4d17a1b5477c80c","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>令狐沖</blockquote><br />\n令狐沖係人都估到但查實係小玄子"},{"pid":"a38e9e5429d61d5b795d351a74318c855f189904","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無忌哥哥乾坤大挪移都夠做啦</blockquote><br />\n但係話華山加崑崙嘅正反兩儀刀劍操得掂<br />\n係比乾坤有過之而無不及喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2720d0d13578608bc8c77e97e30abc50a65f588","tid":205491,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T22:40:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69ad86c26e0fa6c0ba79cb96867b9afcc6ea47ca","tid":205491,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T23:45:03.000Z","msg":"武功一定係楊過<br />\n張無忌我記得去到最後都仲係人前人留落黎既野<br />\n楊過已經去到創自己一套消魂掌既level<br />\n<br />\n內功應該張無忌係金庸小說top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284857fb822c1263d0a699ff99a20db13ce8e007","tid":205491,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>武功一定係楊過<br />\n張無忌我記得去到最後都仲係人前人留落黎既野<br />\n楊過已經去到創自己一套消魂掌既level<br />\n<br />\n內功應該張無忌係金庸小說top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有大挪移有咩招唔係你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7806b33dd6610b5182829632c993c82ec17d25","tid":205491,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>武功一定係楊過<br />\n張無忌我記得去到最後都仲係人前人留落黎既野<br />\n楊過已經去到創自己一套消魂掌既level<br />\n<br />\n內功應該張無忌係金庸小說top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有大挪移有咩招唔係你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你識用同創自己一套既武學修為已經唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話佢練到咁高層既大挪移係武學奇才都仲有得講下"},{"pid":"0739feeece2cf6ac24951d65629c048bde09ec30","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>武功一定係楊過<br />\n張無忌我記得去到最後都仲係人前人留落黎既野<br />\n楊過已經去到創自己一套消魂掌既level<br />\n<br />\n內功應該張無忌係金庸小說top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你又啱喎，唔醒起楊過自家製套掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02702d6916e8bc4ce735b9572cd47cfe72e3693","tid":205491,"uid":43466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T02:54:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/令狐沖潮文\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E4%BB%A4%E7%8B%90%E6%B2%96%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f9a2c85c\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/令狐沖潮文</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bcaed6b5900338f77eb26d8f6ecfad2951b499","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/令狐沖潮文\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E4%BB%A4%E7%8B%90%E6%B2%96%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f9a2c85c\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/令狐沖潮文</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece4ea5559ed98b0ea177980d16500dc9c8fa230","tid":205491,"uid":53577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"段譽，手揸6支槍，内功等於6個一燈大師"},{"pid":"0bd9b115f22a69a5e82e188fd9ac4b2b63b0e9fc","tid":205491,"uid":87303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>段譽，手揸6支槍，内功等於6個一燈大師</blockquote><br />\n我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠打又可以走，你又捉佢唔到"},{"pid":"70f99cd2c133ca9b011051f0adbba3d4b6a9903e","tid":205491,"uid":5288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>段譽，手揸6支槍，内功等於6個一燈大師</blockquote><br />\n我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠打又可以走，你又捉佢唔到</blockquote><br />\n意思即係金庸筆下最勁？"},{"pid":"3e0962a499e43b7ee5dcfcba19ee2e7ca90b2424","tid":205491,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>武功一定係楊過<br />\n張無忌我記得去到最後都仲係人前人留落黎既野<br />\n楊過已經去到創自己一套消魂掌既level<br />\n<br />\n內功應該張無忌係金庸小說top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有大挪移有咩招唔係你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張無忌抄唔到黯然銷魂掌，因為冇野好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非諗住自己老豆老母死於非命啦"},{"pid":"ac98c3d2a15a06cd7dfa48009bbd020300c64efc","tid":205491,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>段譽，手揸6支槍，内功等於6個一燈大師</blockquote><br />\n我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠打又可以走，你又捉佢唔到</blockquote><br />\n以功力計，蕭峰同虛竹都勁過段譽，蕭淨係用掌力已經可以令到段譽用唔到凌波微步；至於虛竹，你段譽吸人幾多內功都唔會多得過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}